posting_body: ['Available September 1:   Harbor Town Apartments is currently offering bright, spacious, 1-bedroom units in an updated mid-century building.', ' Great layout.', 'Excellent Capitol Hill neighborhood with close proximity to both downtown and Madison Park.', ' The property is close to universities, retail, groceries (including Trader Joe’s and Safeway) and public transportation.', ' Common area laundry room located on-site.', 'Please inquire as to availability of additional parking and storage.', 'RENT:  $1545 (2nd floor);  $1595 (3rd floor) per month', 'TO VIEW, please call/ text Kurt at', 'show contact info', '$90 per month Utility Fee covers water/sewer/garbage', '$900 Security Deposit', 'Last Month Rent deposit required', 'Harbortown is a No Smoking/ No Pet property', '*Photos might not be of exact unit available but do represent the general look of units at this property.', '<URL>']
